Current Patch Set: 1&lt;br/&gt;
Commit: 4a61ed82c999a8d4449407de19aa6524a20214cf&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="283442" author="adilger" created="Tue, 27 Oct 2020 21:15:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I agree that this would be very useful.  When this change is made, the code in &lt;tt&gt;lustre/scripts/lnet.in&lt;/tt&gt; should be modified correspondingly:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
-        lustre_rmmod ptlrpc || exit 1
-        lnetctl lnet unconfigure || exit 1
-        lustre_rmmod libcfs ldiskfs || exit 1
+       lustre_rmmod || exit 1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;along with &lt;tt&gt;lustre/scripts/systemd/lnet.service.in&lt;/tt&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
-ExecStop=@sbindir@/lustre_rmmod ptlrpc
-ExecStop=@sbindir@/lnetctl lnet unconfigure
-ExecStop=@sbindir@/lustre_rmmod libcfs ldiskfs
+ExecStop=@sbindir@/lustre_rmmod
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
